text: Tara juna striko gharama yusupha basdathe, usale aphutira akrsta garna khoji ra dhoka thuni bhannathali (yusupha!) Chito a'u. Unale bhane ki allahale, sarana pradana garos, uhi mero palanakarta ho, usale mala'i ramrari rakheko cha nihsandeha atyacari manisaharu kahilyai saphalata prapta gardainan
